Invocation Name: gobble gobble
des: Pretty simple little skill here but super fun for kids and possibly annoying for parents. Just say "Alexa, Gobble Gobble" and she will Gobble like a turkey. Beware though kids will ask her to gobble over and over again for lots of thanksgiving fun.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
